---
source: tests/process.rs
expression: "String::from_utf8(help.get_output().stdout.clone())?"
---
An unofficial Venmo command-line client

Usage: venmo [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  auth             Validate and manage the stored Venmo bearer token
  pay              Pay one person
  request          Create a request immediately
  accept           Accept an incoming request after authoritative validation and confirmation
  decline          Decline an incoming request without sending money
  friends          Inspect friends of the active account
  users            Find Venmo users
  payment-methods  Inspect available payment methods
  balance          Show the Venmo wallet balance
  activity         Inspect account activity
  requests         Inspect pending requests
  doctor           Run read-only diagnostics
  completions      Generate shell completion source
  help             Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -v, --verbose
          Write redacted diagnostics to stderr

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

  -V, --version
          Print version

Financial exit code 3 means the write outcome must be verified independently. Do not retry; check `activity list`, `requests list`, and the official Venmo app.
